# Infrastructure

Deployments and managed services live on **Railway**.

## Services

| Piece | Notes |
| --- | --- |
| Backend API | Fastify in `server/` |
| Web app | Expo web build |
| iOS app | Expo / EAS native (API + assets talk to Railway) |
| Admin web app | `admin_app/` |
| Postgres | Primary DB (`DATABASE_URL`) |
| Redis | Cache / queues (`REDIS_URL`) |
| S3 bucket | Object storage (uploads / media) |

Prefer Railway for deploy, env vars, logs, and ops questions. Do not assume a separate cloud for these pieces unless the user says otherwise.
